{"ja457:0.1":"Jataka ","ja457:0.2":"Ekadasakanipata ","ja457:0.3":"Matuposakavagga ","ja457:0.4":"3. Dhammadevaputtajataka ","ja457:1.1":"“Yasokaro punnakarohamasmi, ","ja457:1.2":"Sadatthuto samanabrahmananam; ","ja457:1.3":"Maggaraho devamanussapujito, ","ja457:1.4":"Dhammo aham dehi adhamma maggam”. ","ja457:2.1":"“Adhammayanam dalhamaruhitva, ","ja457:2.2":"Asantasanto balavahamasmi; ","ja457:2.3":"Sa kissa hetumhi tavajja dajjam, ","ja457:2.4":"Maggam aham dhamma adinnapubbam”. ","ja457:3.1":"“Dhammo have paturahosi pubbe, ","ja457:3.2":"Paccha adhammo udapadi loke; ","ja457:3.3":"Jettho ca settho ca sanantano ca, ","ja457:3.4":"Uyyahi jetthassa kanittha magga”. ","ja457:4.1":"“Na yacanaya napi patirupa, ","ja457:4.2":"Na arahata teham dadeyyam maggam; ","ja457:4.3":"Yuddhanca no hotu ubhinnamajja, ","ja457:4.4":"Yuddhamhi yo jessati tassa maggo”. ","ja457:5.1":"“Sabba disa anuvisatohamasmi, ","ja457:5.2":"Mahabbalo amitayaso atulyo; ","ja457:5.3":"Gunehi sabbehi upetarupo, ","ja457:5.4":"Dhammo adhamma tvam katham vijessasi. ","ja457:6.1":"Lohena ve hannati jatarupam, ","ja457:6.2":"Na jatarupena hananti loham; ","ja457:6.3":"Sace adhammo hanchati dhammamajja, ","ja457:6.4":"Ayo suvannam viya dassaneyyam. ","ja457:7.1":"Sace tuvam yuddhabalo adhamma, ","ja457:7.2":"Na tuyha vuddha ca garu ca atthi; ","ja457:7.3":"Magganca te dammi piyappiyena, ","ja457:7.4":"Vacaduruttanipi te khamami”. ","ja457:8.1":"“Idanca sutva vacanam adhammo, ","ja457:8.2":"Avamsiro patito uddhapado; ","ja457:8.3":"‘Yuddhatthiko ce na labhami yuddham’, ","ja457:8.4":"Ettavata hoti hato adhammo. ","ja457:9.1":"Khantibalo yuddhabalam vijetva, ","ja457:9.2":"Hantva adhammam nihanitva bhumya; ","ja457:9.3":"Payasi vitto abhiruyha sandanam, ","ja457:9.4":"Maggeneva atibalo saccanikkamo. ","ja457:10.1":"Mata pita samanabrahmana ca, ","ja457:10.2":"Asammanita yassa sake agare; ","ja457:10.3":"Idheva nikkhippa sariradeham, ","ja457:10.4":"Kayassa bheda nirayam vajanti te; ","ja457:10.5":"Yatha adhammo patito avamsiro. ","ja457:11.1":"Mata pita samanabrahmana ca, ","ja457:11.2":"Susammanita yassa sake agare; ","ja457:11.3":"Idheva nikkhippa sariradeham, ","ja457:11.4":"Kayassa bheda sugatim vajanti te; ","ja457:11.5":"Yathapi dhammo abhiruyha sandanan”ti. ","ja457:12.1":"Dhammadevaputtajatakam tatiyam. "}